Copyright is automatic.  You write something, it's copyrighted.  There are
ways to register it, but it's not necessary.  The thing that's necessary is
to be able to prove that your wrote it.  The mailing thing is one way of
proving the date that you completed it.  Putting it on the net would be
another way, as long as it remained on the website indefinitely and as long
as you could prove that the website's dates are accurate.  This will only
come up if someone steals your song and you sue them.
